n\nA Dockerized messageboard service that uses two bash scripts as backend and\nnetcat to communicate.\n\nmessage.alessandroferrari.live\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n0 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n1 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases\n\nNo releases published\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Languages\n\n  * Shell 76.8%\n  * Dockerfile 23.2%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
